{"id":1296,"date":"2022-07-20T10:47:06","date_gmt":"2022-07-20T01:47:06","guid":{"rendered":"https://blogbooks.net/?p=1296"},"modified":"2022-07-20T11:26:29","modified_gmt":"2022-07-20T02:26:29","slug":"chromebook-interclass%e3%81%ae%e7%9b%a3%e8%a6%96%e5%9b%9e%e9%81%bf%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/1296/","title":{"rendered":"[Chromebook] InterCLASSの監視回避方法"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"494\" height=\"286\" data-attachment-id=\"1297\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/1296/attachment/screenshot-2022-07-20-10-12-38/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.12.38.png\" data-orig-size=\"494,286\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot 2022-07-20 10.12.38\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.12.38-300x174.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.12.38.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.12.38.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1297\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.12.38.png 494w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.12.38-300x174.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.12.38-64x36.png 64w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 494px) 100vw, 494px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>ChromeProです。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>最近まで、Chromebookに「InterCLASS Cloud 学習者」を入れられていました。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>もう、入れられていない(InterCLASS Filtering Serviceになった)ので、公開しようと思います。</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">注意事項</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">今は、もう利用できるかわかりません。</span></mark></strong></li><li>普通に、めんどくさいです。(いちいちやらなければならない)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">ガイドブック</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>１. 「chrome://flags」と入力して Enter</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"309\" height=\"42\" data-attachment-id=\"1298\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/1296/attachment/image-18/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-18.png\" data-orig-size=\"309,42\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"image-18\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-18-300x41.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-18.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-18.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1298\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-18.png 309w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-18-300x41.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 309px) 100vw, 309px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>２. そうすると、このような画面が出てくるので上の検索で、「Limit Shelf」と入力してください</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"543\" data-attachment-id=\"1300\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/1296/attachment/image-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-20.png\" data-orig-size=\"1366,725\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"image-20\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-20-300x159.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-20-1024x543.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-20-1024x543.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1300\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-20-1024x543.png 1024w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-20-300x159.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-20-768x408.png 768w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-20.png 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>３. そして、「<mark>Limit Shelf</mark>&nbsp;items to active desk」と出てくると思うので、その横にある 選択肢(基本、Defaultって表示されてる)をクリックして、「Enabled」を選択</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"659\" height=\"103\" data-attachment-id=\"1301\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/1296/attachment/image-21/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-21.png\" data-orig-size=\"659,103\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"image-21\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-21-300x47.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-21.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-21.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1301\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-21.png 659w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-21-300x47.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 659px) 100vw, 659px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>４. そして、下に出てる「Restart」(再起動)をクリック</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"975\" height=\"71\" data-attachment-id=\"1302\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/1296/attachment/image-22/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-22.png\" data-orig-size=\"975,71\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"image-22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-22-300x22.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-22.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-22.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1302\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-22.png 975w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-22-300x22.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-22-768x56.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 975px) 100vw, 975px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>５. 再起動し終わったら、デスク切り替えのkey(一番上の右から7番目)を押して、他のデスクにInterCLASSをドラックして</p>\n\n\n\n<p>※ (他のデスクがない場合は、新しいデスクをクリックしてそのデスクにInterCLASSをドラック)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"911\" height=\"365\" data-attachment-id=\"1304\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/1296/attachment/screenshot-2022-07-20-10-32-34/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.32.34.png\" data-orig-size=\"911,365\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.32.34\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.32.34-300x120.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.32.34.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.32.34.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1304\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.32.34.png 911w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.32.34-300x120.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.32.34-768x308.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>６. そうすると、いなくなったと思います(表示だけ)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" data-attachment-id=\"1305\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/1296/attachment/image-24/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-24.png\" data-orig-size=\"1366,768\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"image-24\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-24-300x169.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-24-1024x576.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-24-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1305\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-24-1024x576.png 1024w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-24-300x169.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-24-768x432.png 768w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-24-640x360.png 640w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-24-64x36.png 64w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/image-24.png 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>７. これで、先生が監視を開始したときに、InterCLASSがこのデスクに戻ってくるようになりました(右下に表示されます)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"338\" height=\"56\" data-attachment-id=\"1308\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/1296/attachment/screenshot-2022-07-20-10-30-51/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.30.51.png\" data-orig-size=\"338,56\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.30.51\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.30.51-300x50.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.30.51.png\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.30.51.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1308\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.30.51.png 338w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-20-10.30.51-300x50.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 338px) 100vw, 338px\" /><figcaption>編集めんどくさいから許して</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>８. その度に、InterCLASSをもう一度、他のデスクに移動させ</p>\n\n\n\n<p>そのデスクで、なんでもいいので、タブを開きます。これで、先生には、その開いたタブが表示(先生側がリロード(再読み込み) or もう一度、授業を開始したとき)以外は、対策できましたー</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>(めんどくさいですね)</p>\n\n\n\n<p> -> ちなみに、僕の学校では、時々しか、監視されないので、この方法がめちゃくちゃ有効でした。</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>以上です。ありがとうこざいました。</p>\n",